#Node Affinity

Description: 

Create a busybox Pod which should only be running on node having label app=busybox and should sleep for 3600 seconds

#Solution:

apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  creationTimestamp: null
  labels:
    run: busybox
  name: busybox
spec:
  nodeSelector:
    app: busybox
  containers:
  - image: busybox
    name: busybox
    command: ["/bin/bash", "sh", "sleep 3600"]
    resources: {}
  dnsPolicy: ClusterFirst
  restartPolicy: Never
status: {} 


